WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Welcome to British English Academy A2-M01: Identity, goals and learner profile. Learners practise describe routines and past events through introductions, routines, aspirations, personal information. The teacher models present continuous vs present simple, introduces vocabulary such as personal details, goals, classroom objects, numbers, dates, then learners complete quiz, evidence upload and reflection.
